{"tid":1512924,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又講下警察朋友嘅睇法","createTime":"2019-08-28T05:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T07:25:36.000Z","uid":51740,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e5ef6fe7c6ad2bf5003fa126951f7672508c78","tid":1512924,"uid":51740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:48:18.000Z","msg":"利申，我朋友不是我，但信得過<br />\n<br />\n好多手足發夢喺前線又打又屌d黑警<br />\n黑警就實抵屌唔駛諗，咁正常嘅警察點解前線唔見人？<br />\n<br />\n朋友就咁講，正常嘅警察一早就心灰，盡力調去hea位，講緊最遲係對上雨革<br />\n佢哋一出學堂做新人，只會對老屎忽同上頭唯唯諾諾，小部分到ptu完先開始有自己想法，大部分個腦就留左喺學堂<br />\n<br />\n灰心唔係對個革命，係對警察內部嘅腐敗同官僚作風<br />\n點解黑警一出現總帶一股戾氣？因為佢地重standby 未出黎上gear已經俾班白衫玩撚到透，出黎重點會有好面口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n何況上級個個都叫下面自己執生，未有鑊就諗定點明哲保身，前線咪出現左無證黑警囉<br />\n<br />\n唔係想同黑警洗白，話佢地都係人點點點<br />\n佢哋受得薪就至少包埋受壓力<br />\n但可以嘗試下去分化白衫同藍衫，白衫施壓藍衫懷柔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e435146e427351983ff5217325b3fa45339e7dc","tid":1512924,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:49:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ83u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=00258315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ83u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=6925d6b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ83u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=9e253b7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"f5c3a3da4a03e9f6b36688667baa0b0995735768","tid":1512924,"uid":18354,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:53:16.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩 <br />\n警察唔會再係褒義詞"},{"pid":"e8e7e057c3fcac540f8ee46f583203ebd38b4336","tid":1512924,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uYUDw3Z.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuYUDw3Z.gif&h=d9391fa8&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>民陣雙普選遊行</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6rpDtwf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6rpDtwf.png&h=9ea0b350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LRHQ4Da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLRHQ4Da.png&h=5bc14ba6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手足到時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60e22d8e445ed592ffaa7a190cb9122ffb9b977","tid":1512924,"uid":132088,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:54:57.000Z","msg":"死開啦 毅進仔  <br />\n人又廢 良心又冇埋<br />\n死撚左佢啦 死撚埋右唔該"},{"pid":"ef7844762fda291942273bcf7cd66bb795dbe32c","tid":1512924,"uid":98926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:56:26.000Z","msg":"即係黑警唔止憎示威者 仲將對上司嘅不滿發洩落手足身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果然黑警係垃圾"},{"pid":"1644af749c703924c63fb0f5611aa8fa052240d7","tid":1512924,"uid":258377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:59:31.000Z","msg":"不推"},{"pid":"884781d6a2c909aa01c25104005f336507c07176","tid":1512924,"uid":21259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:06:16.000Z","msg":"死撚開啦死黑警"},{"pid":"09692cfb0abc09e551ed76e6afb691f1e608144c","tid":1512924,"uid":51740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ef7844762fda291942273bcf7cd66bb795dbe32c","tid":1512924,"uid":98926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:56:26.000Z","msg":"即係黑警唔止憎示威者 仲將對上司嘅不滿發洩落手足身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果然黑警係垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:08:28.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\npopo記招同藍絲成日話佢地蒙受巨大壓力，其實有一半係內部仆街作風造成<br />\n<br />\n趁得閒歸納下<br />\n1.警察無腦率保守有70%，前線黑警則超過90%，所以唔好諗住你前面個黑警重有腦會留手，反而交通可能重正常d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.白衫玩鳩藍衫率亦有80%up, 唔知係咪就係士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以佢地內部就算方向一致都唔係絕對團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.如果藍白之間出現矛盾，例如對on9 order(即係連on9都覺得on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)嘅不滿爆發，咁就有花生食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb0e64fcf3f74768d745c8667f8a12aca4d5aa4","tid":1512924,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:10:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警察朋友post一律唔洗睇<br />\n大家善用不推文回覆<br />\n警犬無一個係無辜</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"63fb029fbfaab1c6468681ee926aa04073fa66c1","tid":1512924,"uid":181697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:25:36.000Z","msg":"祝大家升棺發財<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}